{"tid":608944,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"考試局的「考慮因素」","createTime":"2018-03-28T14:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T16:55:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b7fe7d8fb007b97944ebe7e92bda648c9b8d639a","tid":608944,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T14:56:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20180328/20344657\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180328%2F20344657&d=rjVGkcL2WRkkAMqrJz%2F5yp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=b80f5c58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180328%2F20344657&h=76769db2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/daily/article/20180328/20344657</a><br />\n<br />\n考試局的「考慮因素」 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n名采論壇   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20180328/large/e8811a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20180328%2Flarge%2Fe8811a.jpg&h=39b8b51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今年香港中學文憑試中文卷有一條口試題：「家長為子女選擇課餘活動，以下均是考慮因素，試就重要性排列優次：發展興趣，增長知識，強健體魄。」試官原來連中文都不會寫。<br />\n<br />\n按那條試題由現代漢語翻譯成中文，可作「家長為子女選擇課餘活動，須着眼以下三事。試按其輕重，依次排列：培養興趣，增長知識，強健體魄。」原文所謂「優次」，即「優先次序」縮寫，無非英文priority的惡譯。<br />\n<br />\n英文priorities其實是指「按緩急輕重排列的事物」，硬譯做「優先次序」，未免笑話：排於末尾者何「先」之有？「就重要性排列優次」，是英文prioritize the importance的方塊字寫法，怎可說是「中文」。<br />\n而「考慮因素」同樣是英文，即consideration，有時硬譯作「考量」。按consideration固然可以譯做「考慮」，但也可譯做「理由」、「原因」、「須思考的事物」等。<br />\n<br />\n一九七零年版香港世界書局編訂的《英漢四用辭典》consideration條下兩個例句值得參考：「Five pounds is a great consideration for a poor man五鎊對於窮人是很大的數目。」 「I spared him from considerations of mercy我因憐憫之念而恕了他。」現代漢語一定會把這兩句譯做「五鎊對於窮人是一個很大的考慮因素」、「我出於憐憫的考量而恕了他」。過去五十年中文之頹敗，於此可見一斑。<br />\n<br />\n香港教育局以及考試局負責中文科的高官，根本不知中文為何物，難怪他們連「興趣」都要「發展」。"},{"pid":"825f0115c1eb56a3f3a0b487b20a0a6e011b6bb4","tid":608944,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T15:56:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95c5e8cae896917a53b6200372655c33b128aece","tid":608944,"uid":45914,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T16:07:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae2e9aa6c9fff92e9814f29f3cd5c269156e504d","tid":608944,"uid":7840,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T16:18:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"218278476d9a60f29a2da9cd00b50dd114ee56d3","tid":608944,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae2e9aa6c9fff92e9814f29f3cd5c269156e504d","tid":608944,"uid":7840,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T16:18:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T16:45:53.000Z","msg":"即刻見到條題目有咩問題"},{"pid":"bc7fedcb1c6c0c4d065b139c38e56f00906414c2","tid":608944,"uid":161352,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T16:55:32.000Z","msg":"2015年reading 篇文間接回應左呢類筆者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461b202de20d9114619c2c649f4937917b3f6377","tid":608944,"uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T19:06:15.000Z","msg":"咁寫文言文算啦<br />\non 99"},{"pid":"33521c3c4629e3425f44908a268968cc9931aa27","tid":608944,"uid":129039,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"95c5e8cae896917a53b6200372655c33b128aece","tid":608944,"uid":45914,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T16:07:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T19:12:00.000Z","msg":"通識科<br />\n乜乜性<br />\n乜乜化<br />\nCls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b917bdcf94e2963c9c7e4a1a6d757a0b95f7e91b","tid":608944,"uid":29804,"like"